) Command Code TRERS is an extension of Command Code TRDBV developed speciﬁcally for ERS processing. TRERS functions exactly as TRDBV with the added ability to select a return based on the DLN of the latest GTREC command executed by the IDRS user without entering parameters the TRERS command. The primary function of TRERS is to allow on line viewing of tax returns on TRDB from one IDRS session while executing GTREC commands from a second IDRS session. (
